        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hydrogen for Ports Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill supports infrastructure for hydrogen-derived fuels, including ammonia, at ports and in the shipping industry. Specifically, the Department of Energy must establish a program for infrastructure that supports the use of such fuels at ports and in the shipping industry. States, local governments, tribal governments, certain private entities, and other eligible entities may apply for grants.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
